canada current account deficit up in quarter canada 's current account deficit widen to a season adjust 2.27 billion dlr in the fourth quarter from a deficit of 1.94 billion dlr in the third , statist canada said . the shortfal for the full year rose to 8.81 billion dlr from 1985 's 584 mln dlr deficit , the feder agenc said . the agenc said the rise in the merchandis surplu , to 2.77 billion dlr from 2.20 billion dlr in the third quarter , wa more than offset by high deficit in servici and invest . the total non-merchandis deficit grew to 5.04 billion dlr from 4.14 billion dlr . the current account deficit wa 912 mln dlr in the fourth quarter of 1985. in the capit account , not season adjust , there wa a total net inflow of 4.76 billion dlr in the fourth quarter , up from a net inflow of 3.22 billion dlr in the third quarter quarter . the total net capit inflow rose to 13.74 billion dlr in 1986 from 7.68 billion dlr in 1985 .